{"lemma":"سُوقٌ","slug":"سُوقٌ","root":"س.#.ق","root_slug":"س-_-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/س-_-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سُوق","root":"سوق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21290"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%82%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"market","examples":[{"text":"فِي السُّوقِ، يُمْكِنُنَا شِرَاءُ الْفَوَاكِهِ وَالْخَضْرَوَاتِ الطَّازَجَةِ وَالْبَضَائِعِ الْأُخْرَى.","english":"At the market, we can buy fresh fruits, vegetables, and other goods."},{"text":"وَمَا أَرْسَلْنَا قَبْلَكَ مِنَ ٱلْمُرْسَلِينَ إِلَّا إِنَّهُمْ لَيَأْكُلُونَ ٱلطَّعَامَ وَيَمْشُونَ فِي ٱلْأَسْوَاقِ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of سَاقَ (sāqa, “to drive, to conscript”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"driving (of a car)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"draft, conscription"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mobilization"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of سَاق (sāq)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to market"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Aramaic שׁוּקָא / ܫܽܘܩܳܐ (šūqā’, “street, market”), from Akkadian 𒋻 (sūqum, “street”), from Akkadian 𒅆𒀀𒄣 (siāqum, “to become narrow”). Cognate to Hebrew שׁוּק (šūq).\n\nDenominal verb from سُوق (sūq, “market, souq”)."},"ipa":["/suːq/","/suːʔ/","/suːɡ/","/sawq/","/saw.wa.qa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21290","headword_ar":"سُوقٌ","root":"swq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A market, mart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place in which commerce is carried on;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place of articles of merchandise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA:) so called because people drive their commodities thither: (TA:) [in the S unexplained, and in the K only said to be well-known:] of the fem. gender, and masc., (S, Mgh, Msb, K, *) the former in the dial. of the people of El-Hijáz, and the latter in that of Temeem, (S and Msb voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuqaAqN","text_ar":"زُقَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,) the former the more chaste, or the making it masc. is a mistake: (Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asowaAqN","text_ar":"اَسْوَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwayoqapN","text_ar":"سُوَيْقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", confirming the opinion of those who hold"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwqN","text_ar":"سُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be only fem.]: also signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"merchandise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tijaArapN","text_ar":"تِجَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA'ato suwayoqapN","text_ar":"جَاءَتْ سُوَيْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Merchandise came"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwqu AlHarobi","text_ar":"سُوقُ الحَرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thickest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most vehement part"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hawomap","text_ar":"حَوْمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the fight;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHarobi","text_ar":"الحَرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwqapu","text_ar":"سُوقَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the midst thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","TA","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}